I wrote an interpreter for Caml bytecode, you can find it here:
	http://people.darmstadt.netsurf.de/Gerd.Stolpmann/javacaml/
It is not complete, i.e. some language features were left out, but it seems to
be enough for some applications. The interpreter is very slow, perhaps it gets
better if you have a Java compiler producing native code.

Gerd
